Features
Two-Player Mode: Play with a friend in real-time.
Input Validation: Ensures valid moves by checking for empty spots and a valid range.
Win Detection: Detects horizontal, vertical, and diagonal victories.
Draw Scenario: Declares a draw if all spaces are filled without a winner.

Getting Started
Prerequisites
Java Development Kit (JDK) 8 or higher.

Installation
Clone the repository:
git clone https://github.com/Nishithpurohit/tic-tac-toe-java.git

Navigate to the project directory:
cd tic-tac-toe-java

Compile and run the game
javac TicTacToe.java
java TicTacToe
